                     (replace (SELECTION POINT) of SEL with 'LEFT)
                     (\TEDIT.SET.SEL.LOOKS SEL 'PENDINGDEL)
                     (replace (TEXTOBJ BLUEPENDINGDELETE) of TEXTOBJ with T)
                     (\FIXSEL SEL TEXTOBJ)
