                       (SETQ SEL NIL))
              (SHOULDNT "No legal value found in selectq in TEDIT.NEXT"))
          (COND
             (SEL 

         (* There really IS a selection made here, so set up the charlooks for it 
         properly.)

                  (replace (TEXTOBJ CARETLOOKS) of TEXTOBJ with (\TEDIT.GET.INSERT.CHARLOOKS TEXTOBJ
