(\TEDIT.FIND.WC1
  [LAMBDA (TEXTOBJ TARGETLIST TRIALEND# END#)                (* ; "Edited  9-Dec-88 09:52 by jds")
                                                             (* ; 
                                                  "TRIALEND# is where the next char string should go")
